Class GResults

All Implemented Interfaces:
GResultsInterface, java.rmi.Remote, java.io.Serializable
public class GResults
extends java.rmi.server.UnicastRemoteObject
implements GResultsInterface

The class represents the results of a geocode operation. It should never be instantiated by the user, instances of this class are returned by PCMLookup. As this class represents data held by the native server, dispose() must be called when finished with this object to avoid resource leaks.

See Also:
LocalTrip.PCMLookup(java.lang.String, boolean), Serialized Form
